{
  "stem": "23645.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they didn't punch a hole in it, and the thing exploded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was in the corner, because I've moved up to the fire to warm myself up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when this exploded, it exploded on my face, and I had my eyes closed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was in excruciating pain because I had these burns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When I'm tired, you can still see it on my-- in here and in here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But it all healed, and I'll tell you how it healed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because when they opened the doors-- you know, and we were stepping over bodies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Half of us were still alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest were all dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody said, you're in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never heard of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I asked, what's-- what's Buchenwald?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody said, it's a political camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I says, what's political?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a guy behind me says, tell them you're political.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I says, well, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, because it's better than being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You'll live at least two weeks longer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember thinking, is this guy nuts?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In what language were you speaking?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were speaking Polish and Yiddish or-- or German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can hear all these languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, so when we got in and we undressed and went through the showers, before going to the showers-- or no, after the showers-- There was this huge-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it looked like-- like a pool, but much smaller than-- than-- than a regular pool, a swimming pool.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody had to go through there, and it was sort of a white substance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was some sort of a disinfectant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people were going in there, dunking into this, and out they came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- I think it was a disinfectant.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
